1. setup drupal ecommerce kickstart
2. install "epesi_commerce" module
3. Set "multilingual with translations" in structure on:
- content types: "basic page", 
- menus: "main menu"
- taxonomy: "Product category" - set "localize" option
4. /admin/commerce/config/currency/handling - Enable dedicated price fields for Epesi Products - for each currency you support
5. Enable "currency selector" block
5. /admin/structure/types/manage/epesi-products/fields/body - click "Enable translation" and confirm
5. set your contact us, rules pages
6. move your banners, boxes, polls, pages etc. to drupal ads, blocks, polls, pages
7. export newsletters recordset from epesi (it will be deleted)
8. run migration.php
9. set drupal url with administrative user/password in epesi ecommerce administration panel
